{"type": "article", "id": 23671, "title": "Anglepoise® 壁灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-11T08:24:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607162228kcxjrn3Wt56bsK4a.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">Anglepoise® 台灯是 1930 年代生产的一款经典台灯，它拥有一个折叠灯壁和一段弹簧连接，有一种俏皮的工业感，你可以在皮克斯动画片片头看到。这盏台灯至今仍在小批量生产并有无数衍生版本。Anglepoise® 最近推出了可用于户外的铰链式壁灯 Original 1227™，可以选择多种型号，预计 6 月份可出售，售价 180 英镑起，<a href=\"https://www.anglepoise.com/product/original-1227-mini-wall-mounted-lamp\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607162226M5cWFoxJu0r3SmfZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607162227241URyhAT0Kifg6B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607162227SEF94RfzhJ1BKWvb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}